		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Font is set to &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;<br />So if you actually have Lucida Grande, or don't have Verdana, you get a capless I.<br /><br />Meanwhile, the Post font is set to &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;<br />Trebuchet MS has the distinctive slanted M character, and a capless I.

		

		</td>
